e House of Representatives (HoR).\n\nSimilarly, NCP Standing Committee Member and Minister for Drinking Water and Sanitation Mani Thapa said NCP Chairman Prachanda took a wrong decision by breaking the principle of consensus in the party.\n\nThe chief of the party\u2019s cultural wing and central committee member Khagendra Rai argued that all progressive artistes and writers have backed the mainstream party.","title":"Spokesperson Gyawali urges leaders to reunite - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2021/03/153925/","video":[]}
